author: Hannah Osborne
title: Coronavirus Has Acquired Mutations That Could 'Substantially' Change Its Ability to Cause Disease
description: Research from China identified 33 mutations of the SARS-CoV-2 virus, 19 of which were new.
content: The new coronavirus has developed mutations with the potential to "significantly" change the way it causes disease, a team from China has found. Researchers identified 33 mutations in the SARS-CoV-2 virus across 11 patient-derived isolates, 19 of which they s… [+7488 chars]
